-- Heritage Oil Settles Tax Dispute With Uganda, New Vision Newspaper Reports
-- Fred Ojambo
-- 2010-07-20T05:15:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/heritage-oil-settles-tax-dispute-with-uganda-new-vision-newspaper-reports.html

          
          
             Heritage Oil Plc settled an 18
billion Ugandan shilling ($8 million) tax dispute with the
Uganda Revenue Authority, the Kampala-based New Vision reported,
citing Edwin Karugire, a lawyer acting on behalf of the oil
company.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
